title: BONUS: Hyde Trade, Lynch Inury, JAC RB Outlook and Mailbag (Fantasy Football Podcast)
description:
We've got a bonus episode for you as we react to Cleveland's trade of Carlos Hyde to the Jaguars. Is Nick Chubb about to become a stud RB? Who is the best JAC RB rest of season? And we also talk about the OAK situation and wonder if Jalen Richard is a more attractive add than Duke Johnson. We break it all down from all angles and then read a bunch of emails before finishing with some FanDuel advice.
